That could be another reason they thought they "thought they were the one" Meaning they didnt get to dance with the person they wanted. at 0:16, we see 2 women, "Miss freshman year," and "Miss our him in therapy" Which can clarify these could be his exes. Now, "Miss focus on my career" could be the one Olivia is jealous over and and perhaps the somg is about.
